    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180340/extras/4ab136d29c2353b3196cf61efe92f053.avif?t=1748915284\" width=610 height=100 /></span><br><br>多达20把宝剑可供选择，每一把都拥有独一无二的攻击方式。将五行之力融入剑锋，或是以剑为媒催动怨灵之力？剑走何招，皆在一念之间。<br>自由搭配并施展90多种绚丽的剑法招式，高达24个流派可供选择。凝气成剑斩杀强敌，或是掀起血海吞噬一切？招无定式，全凭少侠心意。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180340/extras/a0d263fb3710d1bcdd57e3052dbd19c3.poster.avif?t=1748915284\" width=610 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180340/extras/a0d263fb3710d1bcdd57e3052dbd19c3.webm?t=1748915284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180340/extras/a0d263fb3710d1bcdd57e3052dbd19c3.mp4?t=1748915284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180340/extras/d2a77db2fe5149a38d252b6d5c0a67f3.poster.avif?t=1748915284\" width=610 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180340/extras/d2a77db2fe5149a38d252b6d5c0a67f3.webm?t=1748915284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180340/extras/7a33447a9c0d4549013d469083a5c40b.avif?t=1748915284\" width=610 height=100 /></span><br><br>高达70多种宝物可供收集，提供不同的战斗增益甚至额外的战斗技能；收集掉落的武器炼化词条，每一局都能打造独一无二的绝世神兵。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180340/extras/0eace9bb3440eb92db07119f39016368.poster.avif?t=1748915284\" width=610 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180340/extras/0eace9bb3440eb92db07119f39016368.webm?t=1748915284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180340/extras/a332ea81a78f3a152ea318775b37a6b2.avif?t=1748915284\" width=610 height=100 /></span><br><br>邪魔再世降祸人间，唯有手中利刃可救天下苍生。在各个时空间穿梭，历遍奇遇，解开时空紊乱背后的谜团。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180340/extras/41bbffb2005ba2e625b2ae7a7997599a.poster.avif?t=1748915284\" width=610 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180340/extras/41bbffb2005ba2e625b2ae7a7997599a.webm?t=1748915284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180340/extras/3e9c48a19848410907017562cb0e8d34.avif?t=1748915284\" width=610 height=100 /></span><br><br>贯通奇经八脉，修炼各宗武学。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180340/extras/a69e1f2c1ea0c8b93e7343d3dd0b05d1.poster.avif?t=1748915284\" width=610 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180340/extras/a69e1f2c1ea0c8b93e7343d3dd0b05d1.webm?t=1748915284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>欢迎加入海山官方玩家群一起交流</strong></h2>①群：339130215（已满）<br>②群：572434923（可进）<br>③群：190230422（可进）",
